ZH: 我的办公室里有一个答录机。
EN: There is an answering machine in my office.

ZH: 这个答录机可以记录来电信息。
EN: This answering machine can record incoming call information.

ZH:我经常使用答录机来留言。
EN: I frequently use the answering machine to leave messages.

ZH: 这台答录机是最新的型号。
EN: This answering machine is the latest model.

ZH: 我在商店里买了一台新的答录机。
EN: I bought a new answering machine at the store.

ZH: 答录机的功能非常实用。
EN: The answering machine's functions are very practical.

ZH: 请您在听到嘟嘟声后开始留言，谢谢。
EN: Please start leaving a message after hearing the beep, thank you.

ZH: 这个公司在每个办公室都放置了答录机。
EN: This company has placed an answering machine in every office.

ZH: 答录机已经满了，请及时清理。
EN: The answering machine is full, please clean it out in time.

ZH: 答录机的声音有些杂音。
EN: The answering machine has some background noise in its sound.

ZH: 这个答录机有很长的录音时间。
EN: This answering machine has a long recording time.

ZH: 对不起我没听清楚，请再给我留言。
EN: Sorry, I didn't hear clearly, please leave me another message.

ZH: 答录机的操作方法很简单。
EN: The operation method of the answering machine is very simple.

ZH: 我给你的留言，你有没收到？
EN: Did you receive the message I left you?

ZH: 我只要购买一个新的答录机。
EN: I just need to buy a new answering machine.

ZH: 答录机可以根据预设的时间自动接听电话。
EN: The answering machine can automatically answer calls based on preset time.

ZH: 我喜欢这个答录机的设计风格。
EN: I like the design style of this answering machine.

ZH: 我买了一个带蓝牙功能的答录机。
EN: I bought an answering machine with Bluetooth function.

ZH: 在旅途中，答录机可以随身携带。
EN: The answering machine can be carried along on the journey.

ZH: 让我给你的答录机留言，你可以随时回复我。
EN: Let me leave you a message on the answering machine, and you can reply to me at any time.
